locality: Mt. Nakada. Forested slopes along edge of niaouli savanna.
Upper Tchamba River valley. Just E of Wâo Uni, along new logging road toward Tiapayi. Non-ultramafic substrate. Collected with J. Munzinger, M. Schlessman, L. Vary, A. Mouly & T. Le Borgne.
Ridge between Wedénë and Mt. Grandie. Pine plantation to the north, native forest to the south.
